<title>LIKE A MURMURING STREAM</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tangsang apatin luicha a hung luong,
 A luong zela, a luong zela;
 Nisagang kawmah la ngaihnawp um sa'n,
 A luong aluong zel hi.

[V2]
 Luicha a luong, gi kawm zelin,
 Tuilien zuonin a luong;
 Luicha a luong, gi kawm zelin,
 Thienthona la chuh san.

[V3]
 2. Khal nisa thuok hampa haw hih hingin,
 Hihhalh thakin, Hihhalh thakin;
 Vacha haw leh pakcha haw dawn ding pie'n,
 A sukipak zel hi.

[V4]
 3. Lien deuh deuhin malam na zuon zela,
 Gi hieu hieu in, Gi hieu hieu in;
 Na chiehna chenga vangsakna thu puo'n,
 Gi kawmin luong zelin.

[V5]
 4. Ei haw naupangte le luicha bangin,
 La sa zelin, la sa zelin;
 Lung thieng pu'n, mi lungsiet leh panpih in,
 Lasa'n chieh zel hitiu.</lyrics>
</song>